ttps://twitter.com/shirakamifubuki" target="_blank" rel="noopener">白神吹雪</a>，成员分为上前S组和上前A～B组。</p><p>这一次，各队将在训练结束后接受真正的挑战。采用的规则是加池地区和绳张战斗，两种规则将交替执行。三支球队进行循环赛，五场比赛中先取得三场胜利的球队获胜。您只能使用之前申请的两种武器，并且仅在主装备打开的情况下进行比赛。</p><p>单击此处查看成员列表。</p><blockquote><p> ■冈汤组、冈汤猫又、星町水成、高峰瑠衣、佐花中克洛伊</p><p>■Korone队、犬神Korone、Aki Rosenthal、Natsiro Matsuri、Hosho Marine</p><p> ■吹雪组、白神吹雪、不知火弗莱尔、佐仓巫子、Roboko桑</p></blockquote><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/a885b8c89154c7a6fd043de14d24d60e-kix.m4vcpd6n5542-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/a885b8c89154c7a6fd043de14d24d60e-kix.m4vcpd6n5542-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/a885b8c89154c7a6fd043de14d24d60e-kix.m4vcpd6n5542-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/a885b8c89154c7a6fd043de14d24d60e-kix.m4vcpd6n5542-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/a885b8c89154c7a6fd043de14d24d60e-kix.m4vcpd6n5542-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a><br /> （来自<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_XKb3vB6pYI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">猫又粥 YouTube 频道</a>）</p><p> 《Splatoon 3》是一款射击游戏，玩家们一边互相用墨水绘画一边争夺领地。深受VTuber和主播欢迎的Hololive举办了前作《Splatoon 2》的比赛，VTuber团体“ <a href="https://www.nijisanji.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nijisanji</a> ”也举办了由VTuber赞助的比赛。</p><p> （参考） <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_XKb3vB6pYI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube</a></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/splatoon-hololive/">Hololive后《Splatoon 3》游戏锦标赛正在举办！团队成员通过抽签选出并</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ;
